# Poom

Poom is a video calling application (a Zoom clone) built with [Next.js](https://nextjs.org). It leverages modern web technologies to provide seamless real-time video communication with a responsive user interface.

## Demo

Experience the live demo at: [poom-two.vercel.app](https://poom-two.vercel.app) 

## Features

- **Real-Time Video Calling:** Connect with others using high-quality video calls.
- **Sceduling Video Calls:** Scedule you vide calls for later.
- **Reacording Video Calls:** Record you vide calls to review them late.

## Setting up the project locally

### Prerequisites

- **Node.js:** Version 14 or later is recommended.
- **Package Manager:** npm, yarn, or pnpm.

### Installation

1. **Clone the repository:**

   ```bash
   git clone https://github.com/parham-ghasemi/Poom.git
   cd Poom
   ```

2. **Install dependencies:**

   ```bash
   npm install
   # or
   yarn install
   # or
   pnpm install
   ```

3. **Add Your Environment Variables

   ```
   NEXT_PUBLIC_CLERK_PUBLISHABLE_KEY=
   CLERK_SECRET_KEY=
   NEXT_PUBLIC_CLERK_SIGN_IN_URL=
   NEXT_PUBLIC_CLERK_SIGN_UP_URL=
   NEXT_PUBLIC_STREAM_API_KEY=
   STREAM_SECRET_KEY=
   NEXT_PUBLIC_BASE_URL=
   ```


4. **Start the development server:**

   ```bash
   npm run dev
   # or
   yarn dev
   # or
   pnpm dev
   ```

5. **Open your browser:**  
   Visit [http://localhost:3000](http://localhost:3000) to see the application running.


## Built With

- [**Next.js**](https://nextjs.org)
- [**TypeScript**](https://www.typescriptlang.org) 
- [**Tailwind CSS**](https://tailwindcss.com) 
- [**Clerk**](https://clerk.com)
- [**Shadcn**](https://ui.shadcn.com)
- [**Stream**](https://getstream.io/)